      "book": "Materia"
    },
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You flourish the weapon used in the casting and then vanish to strike like the wind. Choose up to five creatures you can see within range. Make a melee spell attack against each target. On a hit, a target takes [[/r 6d10]] force damage.</p><p>You can then teleport to an unoccupied space you can see within 5 feet of one of the targets you hit or missed.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 6th level or higher, the damage increases by 1d10 for each slot level above 5th.</p><p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 9th or higher, the damage is further increased by your weapon used and the weapon's properties.</p>",
